# AI Examples with Go

## Prerequisites

- docker
- ollama

```bash
brew install ollama
```


Be sure that ollama running as a service in your machine.

```bash
brew services start ollama
ollama list
```



## Examples

### PGVector

```bash
make pgvector-example
go run vectorstores/pgvector/main.go
[{Tokyo map[area:2190 population:38] 0.6732199}]
[]
[]
```
